{"tid":2478871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國、日本將聯合推出印太版「一帶一路」　抗衡中國","createTime":"2021-04-07T11:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T11:40:49.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c930308cfefd0cc4cff1970afe86aa4798b93172","tid":2478871,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"日本首相菅義偉下周訪美，與美國總統拜登舉行美日首腦會談。據《日經亞洲評論》報導，兩人尋求擴大國外基建合作計劃，將推出印太版「一帶一路」計劃，以抗衡中國的「一帶一路」倡議。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，印太版「一帶一路」計劃透過制訂指導原則，支持印太及以外地區發展高質素基建，涉及包括5G網路與潔淨能源技術。<br />\n<br />\n美日將為出資協助他國興建基礎設施提出指導原則，範圍涵蓋投資的先決條件、執行計劃的制度，以及培養當地人才的建議事項；美日也將制定採購標準與維修規範，令技術外流的風險降到最低。<br />\n<br />\n美日希望透過具規範的印太版「一帶一路」，贏得區域各國信任，並與北京在爭奪印太影響力取得優勢。<br />\n<br />\n另外，報導稱，美日同盟除了可能合作建設智慧城市，亦考慮透過基建計劃協助對抗氣候變化，包括在其他國家推廣下一代電池技術與氫能發電。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chi&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=cb089bb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chi</a><del><a href=\"http://natimes.com/realtimenews/20210407004667-260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210407004667-260&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=22197312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">natimes.com/realtimenews/20210407004667-260</a></del>410?chdtv[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本首相菅義偉下星期訪美，與美國總統拜登舉行美日首腦會談。《日經亞洲評論》報道，兩人尋求擴大國外基建合作計劃，將推出印太版一帶一路計劃，以抗衡中國的一帶一路倡議，透過制訂指導原則，支持印太及以外地區，發展高質素基建，涉及包括5G網路與潔淨能源技術。 報道指，日美將為出資協助他國興建基礎設施，提出指導原則，範圍涵蓋投資的先決條件、執行計劃的制度，以及培養當地人才的建議事項；日美也將制定採購標準與維修規範，令技術外流的風險降到最低。日美希望透過具規範的印太版一帶一路，贏得區域各國信任，並與北京在爭奪印太影響力取得優勢。 報道又指，日美同盟除了可能合作建設智慧城市，亦考慮透過基建計劃協助對抗氣候變化，包括在其他國家推廣下一代電池技術與氫能發電。<br />\n<br />\n[url]https://www.881<del><a href=\"http://903.com/news/china/2386155/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%EF%BD%9C%E6%97%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%B0%E5%A4%AA%E7%89%88%E4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F903.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2F2386155%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%258A%259B%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%2589%2588%25E4&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=4bdd123f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">903.com/news/china/2386155/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%EF%BD%9C%E6%97%A5%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%B0%E5%A4%AA%E7%89%88%E4</a></del>%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E6%8A%97%E8%A1%A1%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B[/url]"},{"pid":"99e0a9fb0d80dfda9e11635464986d6047bfd454","tid":2478871,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:33:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdf2f509a399bd0caabef3fddebbdae80f2c3de","tid":2478871,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"monkey國今鋪發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ffef707eaaf689c833b3fa4ee55206096e85b1","tid":2478871,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fdf2f509a399bd0caabef3fddebbdae80f2c3de","tid":2478871,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"monkey國今鋪發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"關鍵一席<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d354e4c0c0b64506fd209fe676f7eb64a1da5d","tid":2478871,"uid":378548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T11:40:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcAhe8CBZbjBFdcxTBnKFdzQRjwewthfrcRB9Vk8NEWxN?filename=30JCWfm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30JCWfm.gif&h=460349da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbc52d21767b6cfbd82ea51ed5fe5ceae2d110f4","tid":2478871,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fdf2f509a399bd0caabef3fddebbdae80f2c3de","ti